name: GODEMPEPE Series 5, Card 1 Rare Pepe Wallet 2016 NFT Counterparty XCP Asset [100 Supply]
description:
GODEMPEPE is Series 5, Card 1 of the iconic Rare Pepe Wallet set [100 Supply]. This legendary collection of NFTs was minted on Counterparty (XCP) in 2016-18, long before the barrage of normie NFTs that we see today. Many Counterparty wallets have been lost over the years, thus circulation is likely far lower than stated. Inspect the goods:

https://xchain.io/asset/GODEMPEPE

Counterparty assets live in the OP_RETURN section of the Bitcoin blockchain and are traded via the XCP Dex.
